        :VolatileFattyAcids ;
    :isDefinedBy "Release of phosphate from intracellular polyphosphate during anaerobic uptake and storage of volatile fatty acids by phosphate-accumulating organisms." ;
    :occursIn :AnaerobicBioreactor ;
